            <title>[PIG-368] User defined Loader functions need a way to get jobconf without going through Slicer</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-368</link>
                <project id="12310730" key="PIG">Pig</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Some user defined loader functions in the current pig release (without types) need the JobConf to build the appropriate RecordReader. Currently they do this in a round about way by using the Slicer. The jobConf should be available from PigInputFormat.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
